                <div class="kicker"><span class="kicker"><a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/section/opinion">OPINION</a>
                    &nbsp;|&nbsp;
            <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/section/opinion/columns">COLUMNS</a></span></div>

                <h1>We put a talking collar on Nugget the dog and it turns out she f**king hates you</h1>
                
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/monday-monday">Monday Monday</a>
                                    
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">January 15, 2018 | 10:05am EST</span>
                                </div>
                            </aside>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-left text-md-right d-print-none">
                            <ul class="social-links list-unsyled list-inline mt-4 mt-md-0">
                                <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://www.dukechronicle.com/article/2018/01/we-put-a-talking-collar-on-nugget-the-dog-and-it-turns-out-she-fking-hates-you" target="_blank" class="sends-events" data-ga-category="Share" data-ga-action="click" data-ga-label="facebook" data-ga-value="CURL"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a></li>
                                <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="http://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https://www.dukechronicle.com/article/2018/01/we-put-a-talking-collar-on-nugget-the-dog-and-it-turns-out-she-fking-hates-you&amp;text=We put a talking collar on Nugget the dog and it turns out she f**king hates you" target="_blank" class="sends-events" data-ga-category="Share" data-ga-action="click" data-ga-label="twitter" data-ga-value="CURL"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a></li>
                                                                <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="mailto:?subject=We%20put%20a%20talking%20collar%20on%20Nugget%20the%20dog%20and%20it%20turns%20out%20she%20f%2A%2Aking%20hates%20you%20|%20The%20Chronicle&amp;message=Check%20out%20this%20article%20from%20The%20Chronicle%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dukechronicle.com%2Farticle%2F2018%2F01%2Fwe-put-a-talking-collar-on-nugget-the-dog-and-it-turns-out-she-fking-hates-you" class="sends-events" data-ga-category="Share" data-ga-action="click" data-ga-label="email" data-ga-value="CURL"><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i></a></li>
                                <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="#" onclick="window.print()" class="sends-events" data-ga-category="Share" data-ga-action="click" data-ga-label="facebook" data-ga-value="CURL"><i class="fas fa-print"></i></a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                
                <div class="article-content w-100 mb-4">
                                            <p>Forget everything you know about Nugget the dog. Not literally. Not everything. There isn’t time for me to start from scratch re-explaining the concept of a dog. But if you think you have the faintest grasp on the inner thoughts of Duke’s canine sweetheart, you are sorely mistaken.</p>
<p>Thanks to an astonishing breakthrough in a joint project between the Duke Department of Neuroscience, the Nobel Prize-winning Department of Computer Science and some guy that makes collars, the world’s first canine translation device has been developed.&nbsp;</p>

                        <div class="inline-ad float-none float-md-left my-4 mr-0 mr-md-4 text-center d-print-none">
                            <!-- START gryphon/ads/rectangle-inline.tpl -->
            <div id="azk18664"></div>
    <!-- END gryphon/ads/rectangle-inline.tpl -->
                        </div>

                        <p>The discovery was met with awe by scientists across the globe, with a professor at Harvard remarking, “This changes everything; the technological feat that they’ve achieved is simply unbelievable.”&nbsp;</p>
<p>Said the man responsible for the collar’s construction, “Yeah I mean it was a pretty straightforward job. I don’t really know why you’re interviewing me—I just made the collar.”</p>
<p>With the equipment set up, Monday Monday sat down for a world-first interview with Duke’s foremost four-legged creature and what followed was nothing short of jaw-dropping:&nbsp;</p>
<p>Nugget: Right let’s get a few things straight—I didn’t serve two tours in Afghanistan so that I could be harassed and used on a daily basis for some pathetic student’s social media capital—</p>
<p>Monday Monday: I’m sorry what?</p>
<p>Nugget: Did I stutter?</p>

                        <div class="inline-ad float-none float-md-left my-4 mr-0 mr-md-4 text-center d-print-none">
                            <!-- START gryphon/ads/rectangle-article-5.tpl -->
        <div id="azk5125"></div>
<!-- END gryphon/ads/rectangle-article-5.tpl -->
                        </div>

                                                                            <p>Monday Monday: No it’s just—I had no idea you served—</p>
<p>Nugget: I spent eight years carrying out scouting and bomb defusal missions in Pakistan.</p>
<p>Monday Monday: I thought you said you were stationed in Afghanistan and did two tours?</p>
<p>Nugget: No I explicitly said, ‘I <strong>didn’t </strong>serve two tours in Afghanistan.’ Keep up.</p>
                            
    
<div class="mc-signup my-4 p-4 text-center " id="mc-container" data-mc="c4087a59c7">
    <h3>Get The Chronicle straight to your inbox</h3>
    <p>Signup for our editorially curated, weekly newsletter. Cancel at any time.</p>
